OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FUS forces carried out fresh strikes on
OL,7,FIran on Wednesday after President
OL,8,FDonald Trump suggested the Islamic
OL,9,FRepublic is "negotiating on fumes".
OL,11,FSpeaking on condition of anonymity, US
OL,12,Fofficials said forces shot down four
OL,13,FIranian one-way attack drones, which
OL,14,Fthey say posed a threat around the
OL,15,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,17,FIt is understood the strike was
OL,18,Flaunched after the Iranian military
OL,19,Ffired four drones at a US commercial
OL,20,Fship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
