CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779966178
OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FThe US military also struck an Iranian
OL,7,Fground control station in the port
OL,8,Fcity of Bandar Abbas that was about to
OL,9,Flaunch a fifth drone, the officials
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FVia the state-run IRNA news agency,
OL,13,FIran's paramilitary Revolutionary
OL,14,FGuard acknowledged the attack in
OL,15,FBandar Abbas and said it launched a
OL,16,Fretaliatory attack on a US air base
OL,17,Fused to launch the assault.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
