OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FIran did not elaborate on where that
OL,7,Fbase was, but it is understood that a
OL,8,FUS military base in Kuwait came under
OL,9,Fattack.
OL,11,FThe Gulf nation said on Thursday that
OL,12,Fit faced a missile and drone attack on
OL,13,FThursday morning, without providing
OL,14,Ffurther details on what had been
OL,15,Ftargeted.
OL,17,FThe new strikes came after US forces
OL,18,Fcarried out what the Pentagon called
OL,19,F"defensive" strikes on missile launch
OL,20,Fsites and minelaying boats in southern
OL,21,FIran on Monday.
