OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FWashington says it has acted with
OL,7,Frestraint with both of this week's
OL,8,Fstrikes, but they represent a
OL,9,Fchallenge to the already fragile
OL,10,Fceasefire with Tehran.
