OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FOngoing negotiations between the US
OL,7,Fand Iran have so far failed to reopen
OL,8,Fthe Strait of Hormuz ` a crucial
OL,9,Fshipping channel through which about a
OL,10,Ffifth of the world's oil and gas
OL,11,Fpassed before the war.
OL,13,FTrump is looking for a settlement that
OL,14,Fwill reopen the Strait and provide him
OL,15,Fwith a credible argument that Iran's
OL,16,Fnuclear capability has been diminished
OL,17,Fenough to declare victory, winding
OL,18,Fdown a conflict that's been
OL,19,Fpolitically unpopular for Republicans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
