CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779966178
OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FHowever, as things stand, Trump also
OL,7,Frisks finding that closure to his war
OL,8,Fof choice comes with an unsatisfactory
OL,9,Fending.
OL,11,FThe emerging deal puts off many
OL,12,Fcritical issues to be resolved later
OL,13,Fand has prompted suggestions within
OL,14,Fthe US, even from some of Trump's
OL,15,Fsupporters, that Iran's hardline
OL,16,Fleaders will emerge from the conflict
OL,17,Fbattered but emboldened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
