CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779966178
OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FIt all comes to a head just as the
OL,7,Fmidterm elections to determine control
OL,8,Fof Congress come into focus, and as
OL,9,FRepublicans worry that rising costs
OL,10,Fand fuel prices are darkening the
OL,11,FAmerican electorate's mood.
OL,13,FTrump has insisted, however, that
OL,14,FNovember's midterm elections in the US
OL,15,Fwon't make him rush into a deal to end
OL,16,Fthe nearly three-month-old conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
