PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779966178
OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FAt a cabinet meeting on Wednesday,
OL,7,FTrump expressed confidence that his
OL,8,Fadministration was making headway on
OL,9,Fsettling the war and dismissed
OL,10,Fconcerns about the midterms.
OL,12,F"They thought they were gonna outwait
OL,13,Fme. You know, 'We'll outwait him. He's
OL,14,Fgot the midterms'," Trump said. "I
OL,15,Fdon't care about the midterms."
OL,17,FTrump acknowledged there's still work
OL,18,Fto do, but he spoke with a measure of
OL,19,Fcertainty that the two sides would get
OL,20,Fthere.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@SO]vD@aOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
