OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779966178
OL,3,CIran retaliates after US launches
OL,4,Cfresh strikes on military targets
OL,6,FHowever, users said service was slow
OL,7,Fand spotty in some areas, with apps
OL,8,Flike YouTube and Instagram heavily
OL,9,Frestricted, as they were before the
OL,10,Fcutoff began during nationwide
OL,11,Fprotests in January.
OL,13,FTheir decision to lift some
OL,14,Frestrictions this week came as
OL,15,Fnegotiators appeared to be closing in
OL,16,Fon a more permanent truce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
